      <div class="stories-content">
        Our education system is not based on practical knowledge; therefore initiatives like HUM become pivotal. In my personal
        experience, I’ve seen many overachieving students fail in the corporate sector due to lack of soft skills like communication,
        positive attitude & capability to work in a team. Moral values & ethics are the fundamentals of any man/woman. Without these
        essential attributes, all worldly achievements become nullified. I am sure this initiative of HUM can make a big difference
        to fill the pragmatic experience gap between the university teachings and professional field.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
