        like this for the betterment of our youth but now you seem to be ahead of me and I'm very happy for that. As I always love
        to help and support our young minds, I would be more than happy to contribute at every phase of this initiative towards collaboration,
        larger presence, workshops, training & entrepreneurship.This can help our youth in many ways. As we all know we are still
        lacking of platforms where they can truly know themselves, what are their key skills and what kind of opportunities are there
        if they choose that particular domain. Well that's just one of the aspects out of so many which I can personally look forward
        to and can lead too. Wish you all a great success and let the HUM enlighten the lives of thousands and lakhs of people.
      </div>
